Package ACO

package ACO
This package contains the classes that implement the Ant Colony Optimization algorithm. It provides an ant colony that contains multiple ants that traverse a graph and find the shortest path between two nodes. The ants communicate with each other by leaving pheromones on the edges of the graph. The pheromones evaporate over time. The ants choose the next node to visit based on the pheromone levels and the distance between the nodes.
